 @* ----- Card Layout ----- *@
                            <span class="pw-del-row__value"> @* Renders inline text or badge content. *@
 @* ----- Page Model Setup ----- *@
                                @Model.QuantityInStock unit@(Model.QuantityInStock != 1 ? "s" : "") in stock @* Displays or uses data from the products model. *@
