                                <i data-lucide="user" style="width:16px;height:16px;stroke-width:2"></i> @* Renders part of the products page markup. *@
                            </div> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
                            <div class="pw-del-row__content"> @* Starts a layout container for this section. *@
 @* ----- Form Fields ----- *@
